1.       Cannot find module "ionic-native"

  （0） npm install @ionic-native/core --save
   
   （1）Install the Needed Plugins：
   
   npm install @ionic-native/camera --save
   
  （2） Add Plugins to Your App's Module
        ...

        import { Camera } from '@ionic-native/camera';

        ...

        @NgModule({
          ...

          providers: [
            ...
            Camera
            ...
          ]
          ...
        })
        export class AppModule { }
